---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Heatmap | MK Stock Lab" activePath="/heatmap">
  <header class="page-header">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Heatmap</p>
      <h1>시장 히트맵</h1>
      <p class="lead">지수와 포트폴리오 히트맵 데이터는 시장 데이터와 포트폴리오 단계 이후 연결합니다.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="tabs" role="tablist" aria-label="히트맵 대상">
    <span class="tab active">KOSPI200</span>
    <span class="tab">KOSDAQ150</span>
    <span class="tab">S&amp;P500</span>
    <span class="tab">NASDAQ100</span>
    <span class="tab">내 포트폴리오</span>
  </div>

  <section class="heatmap-placeholder">
    <p class="eyebrow">색상 기준</p>
    <h2>상승은 초록색, 하락은 빨간색, 보합은 회색으로 표시합니다</h2>
    <div class="heatmap-grid" aria-label="히트맵 예시 셀">
      <div class="heatmap-cell up">AAPL<small>+5.2%</small></div>
      <div class="heatmap-cell flat">MSFT<small>+0.1%</small></div>
      <div class="heatmap-cell down">TSLA<small>-5.4%</small></div>
      <div class="heatmap-cell up">NVDA<small>+3.0%</small></div>
      <div class="heatmap-cell flat">005930<small>-0.2%</small></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
